urdu transliteration text:
Children are very small and innocent, Baba
Bache to bohot chhote huwa karte hai babaHar aik musibat pe gila karte hai babaMe naaz uthane ko kaha kehti hu(n) baba
@HujjatELC

Now who will call Sakina darling,
Baba mere zakhmon ki dawa kon karegaAb jaan sakina ko bhala kon kahegaPehlu me chhupane ko kaha keti hu(n) baba
@HujjatELC
